#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid "Changing the Icon"
msgstr "Ikooni muutmine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change the icon, simply click on the Icon button. A dialog box will "
"appear, which will show you all available icons. Simply click once with the "
"mouse on the icon of your choice, and click <guibutton>OK</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Ikooni muutmiseks klõpsa ikooninupul. Ilmub dialoogikast, mis näitab kõiki "
"saadaolevaid ikoone. Valimiseks klõpsa neist mõnel ja seejärel nupul "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:200
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
